<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="herself-pron">herself <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hɜː'self/    美 /hɜːr'self/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>她自己；她亲自：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She hurt herself.
她伤着了自己。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She told me the news herself.
她亲口告诉我这个消息。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She's not quite <strong>herself</strong> today<strong>'s not </strong>
她今天不太舒服/情绪不好。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Catherine bought a postcard of the place she was visiting, addressed it to <strong><em>_</em></strong>_(her) and then posted it at the nearby post office.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. herself  </p></div>